---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const updated = "2026-02-24";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Terms of Service — MinimalDev"
  description="Terms of Service for using MinimalDev free online tools and website features."
  canonicalPath="/legal/terms/"
>
  <div class="container">
    <h1 class="page-title">Terms of Service</h1>
    <p class="note">Last updated: {updated}</p>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Acceptance of terms</h2>
      <p>
        By accessing or using MinimalDev, you agree to these Terms of Service.
        If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you should not use the site.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Nature of the service</h2>
      <p>
        MinimalDev provides browser-based tools such as calculators, converters, generators,
        and formatting utilities. Each tool is designed for a specific purpose and is intended
        to provide quick results based on user input.
      </p>
      <p class="note">
        Tools are provided for general informational and practical use and are not intended
        to replace professional advice in areas such as finance, health, or legal matters.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Use of the tools</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>You may use the tools for personal or business purposes.</li>
        <li>You agree not to misuse the site, including attempting to disrupt, overload, or abuse the service.</li>
        <li>You agree not to use automated systems in a way that negatively affects site availability.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>User responsibility</h2>
      <p>
        You are responsible for how you use the results generated by the tools.
        While reasonable effort is made to ensure tools behave correctly,
        outputs may not be suitable for every use case or environment.
      </p>
      <p class="note">
        You should verify results independently when accuracy is critical,
        especially for financial, technical, or decision-making purposes.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>No warranties</h2>
      <p>
        The site and its tools are provided on an “as is” and “as available” basis.
        MinimalDev makes no guarantees regarding accuracy, completeness,
        reliability, or availability of any tool or result.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p>
        To the maximum extent permitted by law, MinimalDev is not liable for any damages
        resulting from the use or inability to use the site, including indirect,
        incidental, or consequential damages.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Service availability</h2>
      <p>
        The site may be updated, modified, or temporarily unavailable at any time without notice.
        Features, tools, or pages may be added, changed, or removed as part of ongoing maintenance or improvement.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Advertising and third-party links</h2>
      <p>
        The site may display advertisements or include links to third-party services.
        MinimalDev is not responsible for the content, policies, or practices of third-party providers.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p>
        These Terms of Service may be updated from time to time.
        Continued use of the site after changes are made indicates acceptance of the updated terms.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p class="note">
        If you have questions about these Terms, please use the
        <a href="/legal/contact/">Contact</a> page.
      </p>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>